stateDiagram-v2

[*] --> Draft

Draft --> Review : submit

Review --> Validation : approved for validation

Review --> Draft : changes requested

Validation --> Testing : schema & safety passed

Validation --> Draft : validation failed

Testing --> Canary : integration tests passed

Testing --> Draft : tests failed

Canary --> Production : rollout approved

Canary --> Draft : rollback

Production --> Deprecated : replaced by newer version

Deprecated --> Archived : retention expired

Archived --> [*]